as been\ndeemed over, implying the likelihood of future outbreaks should the currently\nimposed strict government actions be relaxed. This could make COVID-19 evolving\ninto a long-term epidemic or a community disease a real possibility, suggesting\nthe necessity to conduct universal testing and monitoring to identify the\nhidden individuals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Mar 2020 16:50:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-27"}
