y\nreformulating the OAFP equation in several ways, we improve the accuracy of the\nspectral solution and reproduce an existing self-similar solution, which infers\nthat existing solutions have only one significant figure at best.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Mar 2020 01:08:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Apr 2020 23:30:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
