sing ZF precoding compared to the no-precoding\nscenario for some specific nodes' positions. All the derived analytical\nexpressions are validated through Monte Carlo simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Mar 2020 12:19:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-30"}
